;font-weight:bold" class="text-[16px] lg:text-[18px] leading-[24px] lg:leading-[26px] font-inter lg:font-bold"><p class="!font-semibold lg:!font-bold">Founded in 2015, <?=$namehost?> offers a new way of collaborating to build stronger brands through social media channels. It brings teams together into one central hub to schedule content, deliver through a social inbox, measure performance, monitor brand health and competitors.</p></div><div style="color:#3a4347;font-weight:normal" class="text-[16px] lg:text-[18px] leading-[24px] lg:leading-[26px] font-inter lg:font-bold">From humble bootstrapped beginnings, <?=$namehost?> has steadily grown. We challenge ourselves to give our customers what matters to them the most and, over the past few years, have quickly grown to build long-lasting partnerships with global enterprises and digital agencies. </div><div style="color:#ff5c72;font-weight:bold" class="text-[16px] lg:text-[18px] leading-[24px] lg:leading-[26px] font-inter lg:font-bold"><p class="!font-semibold lg:!font-bold">With headquarters in London, we are a distributed team of 9 people from 4 different countries, helping to manage 12,000+ social media accounts around the globe.<!-- --> <span class="text-gray-1 !font-normal">Behind every product are people: a team and customers. We are delighted to be surrounded by those who believe in our mission and bring experiences to make our product stand out.</span></p></div></div></section><section class="-mt-2.5 lg:-mt-10">
        
        
        
